---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
// Add your new images here
import howItWorks1 from '../assets/howitworks1.jpg';
import howItWorks2 from '../assets/howitworks2.jpg';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="How It Works | New Leaf Academy" description="Our simple, supportive process for starting your tutoring journey with New Leaf Academy." />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>How It Works</h1>
			<p class="intro-text">
				Starting your journey with us is simple, transparent, and designed to ensure the perfect fit for your child. Hereâ€™s a step-by-step look at our process, from our first chat to ongoing success.
			</p>

			<div class="process-grid">
				<div class="process-row">
					<div class="steps-column">
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">1</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Initial Contact</h3>
								<p>Reach out to us via our consultation form, email, or phone. We're ready to listen and answer any initial questions you may have.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">2</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Discovery Chat</h3>
								<p>We'll schedule a friendly, informal chat to discuss your child's specific needs, learning style, and academic goals in detail.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">3</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Free Taster Session</h3>
								<p>We'll book a complimentary 30-minute taster session. This is a great chance for your child to meet their tutor and experience our teaching style firsthand, with no obligation.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="image-column">
						<Image src={howItWorks1} alt="A student engaged in an online tutoring session" class="process-image" />
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="process-row">
					<div class="image-column">
						<Image src={howItWorks2} alt="A tutor explaining a concept on a whiteboard" class="process-image" />
					</div>
					<div class="steps-column">
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">4</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Tailored Learning Plan</h3>
								<p>After the taster session, we'll work with you to decide on the best course of action and create a personalized learning plan tailored to your child's goals.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">5</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Regular Tutoring Sessions</h3>
								<p>With a plan in place, regular one-to-one sessions will begin, focusing on building knowledge, skills, and confidence in a supportive environment.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">6</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Ongoing Support & Feedback</h3>
								<p>We believe in a partnership. You'll receive consistent progress updates and we'll stay in close communication to ensure we're always working together for your child's success.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-section">
				<h2>Still Need Help?</h2>
				<p>Our expert tutors are ready to provide the one-to-one support your child needs. Book a free consultation to get started today!</p>
				<a href="/consultations" class="cta-button">
					Book Your Free Consultation and Taster Session
				</a>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		--card-bg-color: #f9f9f9;
		--box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	main {
		max-width: 1200px; /* Widen the main container for the new layout */
		margin: 2em auto;
		padding: 0 1em;
		box-sizing: border-box;
		color: var(--accent-light);
	}

	h1, .intro-text {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--accent-light)
	}

	.intro-text {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto 3em;
		font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
	}

	.steps-column {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5em;
	}

	.step {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5em;
	}

	.step-number {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		width: 50px;
		height: 50px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background-color: var(--accent);
		color: white;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.2em;
		z-index: 1;
		border: 4px solid #fff;
	}

	.step-content {
		background-color: var(--card-bg-color);
		padding: 1.5em;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		flex-grow: 1;
	}

	.step-content h3 {
		color: var(--accent);
		margin: 0 0 0.5em 0;
		font-size: clamp(1.3em, 3vw, 1.5em);
	}

	.step-content p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	
	.image-column {
		display: none; /* Hide images on mobile by default */
	}

	.process-row {
		margin-bottom: 3em;
	}

	/* --- DESKTOP LAYOUT --- */
	@media (min-width: 1024px) {
		.process-row {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 3em;
		}

		.image-column {
			display: block; /* Show images on desktop */
			padding: 1em;
		}

		/* This makes the second row reverse its column order */
		.process-row:nth-child(2) .steps-column {
			order: 2;
		}

		.process-image {
			width: 100%;
			height: auto;
			border-radius: 12px;
			box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		}
	}

	.cta-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin: 4em auto 0;
		padding: 2.5em;
		background-color: white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		color: var(--accent);
		max-width: 900px;
	}
	
	.cta-section h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
		margin-top: 0;
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	.cta-section p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}

	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1em 2em;
		background-color: var(--accent-pop);
		color: white;
		font-weight: bold;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.cta-button:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}
</style>